You can import detectors directly when you have a Window reference:

import { isMobile, isIOS, isAndroid, isChrome, isSafari, isPWA, isElectron, isTablet, matchMedia, PLATFORMS_MAP } from '@acorex/core/platform';

const mobile = isMobile(window);
const tablet = isTablet(window);

PLATFORMS_MAP mirrors the keywords accepted by platform.is(). Prefer platform.is() in Angular code for automatic SSR handling.
